title: Mama Ines
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Mediterranean, Bakery, Spanish, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Cafe offers some vegan items, including sobresada, hummus and guacamole, in addition to soy milk for coffee/tea. Also operates a bakery in Mercado de Feria which offers a range of breads and sweets/pastries, of which a number of the cakes/pastries served are vegan.
